\contentsline {table}{\numberline {3.1}{\ignorespaces Hardware/software partitioning of the TinyLlama inference pipeline. Operations marked PL are executed in the programmable logic accelerator kernel; operations marked PS run on the ARM Cortex-A53.}}{19}{table.caption.57}%
\contentsline {table}{\numberline {3.2}{\ignorespaces Memory hierarchy of the TinyLlama inference accelerator on the ZCU102. Weight and KV cache sizes are after INT8 quantisation. On-chip buffers are reused across all 22 layers.}}{21}{table.caption.59}%
